---
// src/components/Experience.astro
---

<section class="w-full py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-brand-light dark:bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden flex items-center min-h-screen">
  
  <div class="absolute right-[-50%] md:right-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] md:w-[600px] h-[600px] md:h-[600px] opacity-[0.1] pointer-events-none animate-[spin_120s_linear_infinite]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white rotate-0"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white rotate-45"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-12 border border-white rotate-[22.5deg]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-12 border border-white -rotate-[22.5deg]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-32 border-2 border-brand-gold rotate-45"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-48 border border-brand-gold rotate-0"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <span class="text-brand-gold font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block font-semibold">
        Our Experience & Capabilities
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        What We Bring Into This Work
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16">
        This project is built on years of lived practice and real-world experience:
      </p>

      <div class="pl-6 border-l-2 border-brand-gold/50 relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-0 w-2 h-2 bg-brand-gold rotate-45"></div>
        <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white italic leading-snug">
          "We do not present ourselves as a large institution—but as a small family continuing a craft with the tools we have learned over time."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-4 lg:pl-12">
      
      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Over a decade of life and service in Türkiye as a family
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Long-term practice in traditional Khatam craftsmanship
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Experience in documenting our craft process through video content
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          A previously active online presence where we shared our work journey
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Practical understanding of digital tools such as website creation and UX/UI design
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 group bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 p-6 rounded-lg hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
        <div class="mt-1.5 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-brand-gold rotate-45 shrink-0 group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-125 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <p class="font-sans text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Familiarity with online platforms and content-based outreach
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>